{
  "texts": [
    "We curated natural language description of DWD identifiers (i.e., QIDs) and constructed documents to store in the vector database.",
    "We use QIDs as the document identifier and use LLMs to disambiguate mentions to topranked QID.",
    "GraphAide also generate UMAP embeddings of vector database to visualize the clusters of topics discussed in the KG, as shown in Figure 2.",
    "GraphAide's curation phase processed 1,846 news articles and generated a KG, as shown in Figure 3.",
    "An ontology-guided and WikiData-based disambiguation agent extracts entity mentions from the text and performs RAG-based node re-ranking to identify the closest matched QID."
  ]
}